\b 1. SITE OVERVIEW
\par\par

Unova is a hybrid blockchain and Web3 infrastructure for the real-world economy. It automates trust and verifies business data via smart contracts, ensuring privacy without central authorities. Tagline: "A Web3 Infrastructure for the Real-World Economy."
\par

The site has four main sections: About, Solution, Community, and Build. Each section has sub-pages linked from the main navigation (mega menu) and footer on every page.
